<div class="content" name="FSSAGENT_SHARE_MAPPING" uuid="8bf625df-4d5d-4301-a568-03a902415a5d"><p>The <b>FSSAGENT_SHARE_MAPPING</b> union contains mapping
information for a share to its <a href="0856b278-46f4-4f3e-bc06-bc382b26428b#gt_34537940-5a56-4122-b6ff-b9a4d065d066" data-linktype="relative-path">shadow copy</a> based on the
level value.</p><dl>
<dd>
<div><pre> typedef [switch_type(unsigned long)] union _FSSAGENT_SHARE_MAPPING {
     [case(1)]
         PFSSAGENT_SHARE_MAPPING_1 ShareMapping1;
     [default]
         ;       
 } FSSAGENT_SHARE_MAPPING, *PFSSAGENT_SHARE_MAPPING;
</pre></div>
</dd></dl><p><b>ShareMapping1:</b>  A pointer to an <b>FSSAGENT_SHARE_MAPPING_1</b>
structure, as specified in section <a href="665c2d2b-5ad7-4831-9bea-b21a3d219311" data-linktype="relative-path">2.2.1.1</a>.</p></div>